```markdown
# 🧠 Smart Complaint Management System

A clean and powerful web platform to **file, manage, and resolve complaints** — built for admins, staff, and users.  
Built with 💙 by **Sachin**, using modern tech like React, Tailwind, and Supabase.

---

## 🌟 Features

- 📝 **File Complaints**: Users can submit complaints through an easy-to-use form.
- 📬 **Real-time Access**: Instantly view complaint status and updates.
- 🔐 **Authentication**: Sign up, sign in, and role-based access — powered by **Supabase Auth**.
- 🧑‍🔧 **Staff Dashboard**: View assigned complaints, update status, and resolve issues.
- 🧑‍💼 **Admin Panel**: Full control to manage all complaints, users, and staff assignments.
- 📈 **Scalable & Secure**: Backed by Supabase — PostgreSQL + Edge Functions.

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

| Layer        | Tech                         |
|--------------|------------------------------|
| 💡 Frontend  | [React](https://reactjs.org/) + [Vite](https://vitejs.dev/) |
| 🎨 Styling   | [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com/) + [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com/) |
| 🧠 Language  | TypeScript                   |
| 🗂 Backend   | [Supabase](https://supabase.io/) (Database + Auth) |

---

